column5: Squid and I will be there at 11:00 and will probably spend the whole day wandering around and taking in a couple seminars.  Anybody else gonna be there today ??
Lew,   I took a day off -- hope to see you there.  If you are interested in sharing a ride, reply here and we can set something up ... we are only 3 minutes apart!  Mark
Might be better if we just meet up at the show Mark, as I think we may be there most of the day and into the evening, but plans may also change thru the day and I can't be sure.
Lew,  Not a problem C U there.  Take care.
BE THERE TOMOR AND ALL WEEKEND MYSELF WORK IN THE TIGHTLINES BOOTH!!! HOPE TO RUN INTO SOME NEW AND OLD OFNERS!!!
My buddy and I will be there!
Would really have liked to have gone today Lew, however we working stiffs can't have it our own way all of the time.  Have a great day and say Hi to Pete for me.
Hi Lew Hope to see you there today. I will be with my son in law my fishing bud. Steve
I'll be there in the afternoon for a couple of the seminars. See ya there!
I WILL BE THERE!!  I'll be one with the Jedi hoodie double hauling on the casting platform.  WUUUUUTT!!  Hope to you see you there Lew.  HD
If I get anytime out "for good behaviour" I'll be taking another shot at Simcoe Perch. The schedule is just not working out this year to take in the show.
I was there and to say the least rather disappointed !!!!!  Not a very good show at all.
you wouldnt happen to be nick would ya

Did he have a booth?  If he was casting crisp, it wasn't me LOL  Name's Fidel!  I Was there to test out the new Scott A3s...  Tried an 8w 10ft and it was like buttah.  So I blew a wad and treated myself!     Now I gotta put out..  HD
LMAO at putting out lol thats funny....feed some starbucks cofffee and it will work out
